&lt;p&gt;The team at Advanced Space is leading humanity back to the Moon and pioneering innovative solutions in the space industry. Based in Westminster, Colorado, this incredible team is looking for a Sr. Spacecraft Navigation Engineer who’s eager to push the state of the art in spacecraft navigation technology.&lt;/p&gt;
