&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication, with a record of leading technical presentations and navigation analysis reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;US. Person (U.S. citizen or lawful permanent resident), able to work on-site in Westminster, CO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt

